                        <li><strong>Select a Registered Agent: </strong> The majority of countries demand a local agent or representative to take care of legal formalities and continued compliance. This is necessary in the effort of a hassle-free international business establishment.</li>
                        <li><strong>Applications and Suing Fees: </strong> Hand in the incorporation application to the concerned authorities with all the required documents and pay the registration fees. Confirmation and confirmation of your foreign company formation process.</li>
